<%- include('header') -%>
    <title>Mental Health Tips | MentalMed</title>



    <section class="mental-health-tips container mt-5">
        <h1>Mental Health Tips</h1>
        <p>Improving your mental health is a continuous journey. Here are some tips to help you maintain and enhance your emotional well-being:</p>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3>1. Practice Mindfulness</h3>
                <p>Mindfulness involves being present in the moment and fully engaging with your current experience. It can help reduce stress and improve focus.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3>2. Stay Active</h3>
                <p>Regular physical activity can boost your mood, reduce anxiety, and improve your overall mental health.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3>3. Maintain a Healthy Diet</h3>
                <p>A balanced diet rich in fruits, vegetables, and whole grains can positively affect your mood and energy levels.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3>4. Get Enough Sleep</h3>
                <p>Quality sleep is crucial for mental health. Aim for 7-9 hours of sleep each night to help your body and mind recover.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3>5. Connect with Others</h3>
                <p>Building and maintaining strong relationships can provide emotional support and reduce feelings of loneliness.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3>6. Set Realistic Goals</h3>
                <p>Setting achievable goals can give you a sense of purpose and accomplishment, boosting your self-esteem.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
